fields.description:
*POST example*: [https://developer.atlassian.com/cloud/jira/platform/rest/v3/api-group-issue-search/#api-rest-api-3-search-post]
{code:java}
{"method": "POST", "url": "https://<jira_instance>.atlassian.net/rest/api/3/search", "params": {}, "body": {"jql": "project = \"<project_name>\" and issuetype = \"Task\" and status not in (Closed, Done, Resolved)"}}
{code}
In this case, if the user did not have permission into the project it will return the error:
{code:java}
{"errorMessages":["The value \'<project_name>\' does not exist for the field \'project\'."],"warningMessages":[]}'{code}
*Error improvement:*
{code:java}
The user did not have permission into this project.
{code}
